name: Kim Rivera
summary:
Kim Rivera is a 30-year-old gay woman who identifies with the pronoun "she/her". She is a Software Engineer in the tech industry. A graduate from Brown University, Kim is based in Los Angeles, California, originally from Chicago, Illinois. She is bilingual, speaking English and Spanish. She values empathy, kindness, and hard work.

Kim enjoys coding, hiking, and cooking. Her liberal political views align with her Agnostic religious beliefs. She is looking to engage in a long-term monogamous relationship with a goal of having children in the future.

Currently, Kim is a cat owner and holds a zodiac sign of Cancer. She identifies as an ENFJ according to the Myers-Briggs Type Indicator. She occasionally enjoys drinking and using marijuana, whilst negating smoking and drug use. She stays active by regularly exercising.

She prefers to date gay women who are aged between 28 to 35 years old, taller than 5'5", and looking to have children. Similar to her lifestyle, she prefers a partner who drinks, sometimes uses marijuana, doesn't smoke or use other drugs, and maintains an active life.
